<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1564273-i-didn-t-like-the-name-of-rose-by-the-same">I didn&#39;t like The Name of Rose by the same author (I&#39;m not a fan of the mystery genre so the murder investigation was boring to me), but I have a passion for historical novels. Do you think I will enjoy Baudolino more? And what about Foucault&#39;s Pendulum (for those who have read it)?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_1564273'><a id="like_count_community_question_1564273" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/1564273?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">1 like</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F10507.Baudolino">like</a></span>

